{"tid":2405884,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"【香港開電視】年初一至年初八《便利店新星》池昌旭 金裕貞","createTime":"2021-02-12T17:29:34.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-20T07:55:30.000Z","uid":210261,"like":5,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"741304a80a07d9dcd833f37aacc60f12985267b0","tid":2405884,"uid":210261,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-12T17:29:34.000Z","msg":"【最強顔值CP】<br />\n<br />\n香港開電視誠意為你送上由擁有最強顏值嘅 #池昌旭 同埋 #金裕貞 主演嘅韓劇《便利店新星》。<br />\n暖男崔大賢（池昌旭 飾）開咗間24小時便利店一腳踢，最後頂唔順要請Part Time返嚟幫手，搵著丁新星（金裕貞 飾）呢位惡女店員，天使面孔卻有魔鬼&hellip;性格！首集即獻吻崔大賢，嚇到呢位純情暖男失魂報上電話號碼，自此上演女追男嘅戲碼。不過崔大賢當時已經有女友劉妍珠（韓善伙 飾），究竟佢會點見招拆招？<br />\n<br />\n📺特別播放時間<br />\n2月12日（年初一）深夜1時至4時<br />\n2月13日（年初二）至2月18日（年初七）深夜12時30分至3時30分<br />\n2月19日（年初八）深夜1時至3時<br />\n<br />\n&copy; SBS"},{"pid":"cde3e26fa0606ca6c1d24c507991f711e6b37077","tid":2405884,"uid":210261,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-12T17:45:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WAe85wk.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWAe85wk.jpg&h=c2a27767&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f6a0b99f8ff0143339bfafadf527438e94587ec7","tid":2405884,"uid":210261,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-12T18:01:20.000Z","msg":"第二集<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"22e6fb297f4854221aa903016188531f06e968e9","tid":2405884,"uid":361557,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-12T18:25:57.000Z","msg":"每日3集播得咁急嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c229a89bdce48a04de5bd9efd61ffbc9b080e523","tid":2405884,"uid":210261,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"22e6fb297f4854221aa903016188531f06e968e9","tid":2405884,"uid":361557,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-12T18:25:57.000Z","msg":"每日3集播得咁急嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-12T18:30:49.000Z","msg":"新年深宵特備節目"},{"pid":"932de871e28a85bd92